15
00:04:57.381 --> 00:04:59.800
<i>Meskipun ada banyak rumor,</i>

16
00:04:59.883 --> 00:05:02.594
<i>Saya diam mengenai hal itu</i>

17
00:05:03.387 --> 00:05:04.888
<i>karena aku</i>

18
00:05:05.472 --> 00:05:09.727
<i>dalam situasi dimana aku harus diam</i>
